]</strong><br /> <strong>10. 蓝天的贾人 [ft.绿茶彭]</strong><br /> <strong>11. 我音乐的未来 [ft.整蛊和玛塔]</strong><br /> <strong>12.再见</strong></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/posthumous-lee-scratch-perry-album-announced-with-greentea-peng-feature-released-3540309">Lee 去世后的“Scratch”Perry 专辑与 Greentea Peng 专题一起发布，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
詹姆斯·布朗特谈参观凯莉·费雪的家如何激发了向她致敬的新歌https://www.nme.com/news/music/james-blunt-on-how-a-visit-to-carrie-fishers-house-inspired-new-tribute-song-to-her-3540295?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=詹姆斯·直言不讳地谈论如何访问嘉莉·费舍尔的房子，激发向她致敬的新歌Anagricel DuranWed, 15 Nov 2023 19:53:34 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3540295 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt-and-Carrie-Fisher.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="詹姆斯·布朗特和凯丽·费雪。图片来源：Debbie Hickey 和 Paul Archuleta，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt-and-Carrie-Fisher.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt-and-Carrie-Fisher-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt-and-Carrie-Fisher-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt-and-Carrie-Fisher-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt-and-Carrie-Fisher-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt-and-Carrie-Fisher-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 2003 年，这位歌手前往洛杉矶进一步发展自己的事业，并与这位《星球大战》女演员同居。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/james-blunt-on-how-a-visit-to-carrie-fishers-house-inspired-new-tribute-song-to-her-3540295">詹姆斯·布朗特 (James Blunt) 的帖子讲述了拜访凯丽·费雪 (Carrie Fisher) 的家如何激发了向她致敬的新歌曲，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt-and-Carrie-Fisher.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="詹姆斯·布朗特和凯丽·费雪。图片来源：Debbie Hickey 和 Paul Archuleta，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt-and-Carrie-Fisher.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt-and-Carrie-Fisher-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt-and-Carrie-Fisher-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt-and-Carrie-Fisher-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt-and-Carrie-Fisher-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/James-Blunt-and-Carrie-Fisher-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/james-blunt">詹姆斯·布朗特 (James Blunt)</a>透露，他最新唱片中的歌曲《黑暗思想》(Dark Thought) 的灵感来自于对已故凯莉·费雪 (Carrie Fisher) 故居的参观。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/james-blunt-nme-worst-album-carrie-fisher-who-we-used-to-be-3534073">詹姆斯·布朗特：“有时我看着自己，心想，‘我会打你的脸’”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌曲收录在布朗特的第七张录音室专辑《我们曾经是怎样的人》中。这位歌手在他的新回忆录《<i>松散地基于一个编造的故事》中分享说，</i>这位《星球大战》偶像是他一生中的一个重要人物。在成名之前，费舍尔把布朗特安置在她洛杉矶的住所里，并在她的浴室里录制了他的热门民谣《再见我的爱人》。</p><p>布朗特解释说，“黑暗思想”描述了费舍尔死后他回到那所房子的那一刻。她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/carrie-fisher-cause-of-death-2089749">于2016年12月去世</a>，享年60岁。</p><p>在谈到<em>《NME</em><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/in-conversation">对话</a>》系列中《黑暗思想》的创作时，布朗特说道：“她去世已经有大约七年了，我不太确定，但我花了所有的时间来写为她唱的一首歌。作为一名歌曲作者，最诚实的歌曲通常是最容易写的，因为它只是从你的内心流淌出来。但多年来我一直在思考这首歌，因为她是一个令人难以置信的人。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="詹姆斯·布朗特 (James Blunt) 谈凯丽·费雪 (Carrie Fisher) 的新书，并最终获得 NME“最差专辑”奖" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3nNk2fePugw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他继续说道：“所以我对这首歌所做的只是描述了她死后我回去寻找她的那一刻。我一时兴起回到她家，开车到她家门口，把手放在门上，只是想感受一下她在那里的感觉。我写了关于那一刻的歌曲。”</p><p> “讽刺的是，当我这样做并流下眼泪时，一辆满载游客的敞篷货车停在了屋外，”他说。 “导游说：‘在你的左边，你会看到已故的伟大的凯莉·费雪的房子。 And as you can see, some fans are still deeply moved by her passing.&#39; And that was me.”</p><p> He also recently <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/james-blunt-on-living-with-carrie-fisher-she-became-my-best-best-friend-3519024">shed light on his experience living with the actress in Los Angeles</a> .</p><p> “I was invited to the restaurant 192 in Notting Hill. I was going out with a girl whose parents were family friends of Carrie&#39;s and I sat beside her at lunch,” he told <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2023/oct/21/james-blunt-looks-back-boarding-school-carrie-fisher" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>The Guardian</em></a> . “I had just got a record deal and was moving to LA. Carrie&#39;s first question was: &#39;What do you do?&#39; I said: &#39;I&#39;ve left the army to go to make an album in LA.&#39; Question number two was: &#39;Where are you going to live?&#39; I said I didn&#39;t know. Her reply – the third thing she ever said to me – was: &#39;Well, you&#39;re going to live with me.&#39; So I did just that.</p><p> He continued: “For the first month, I didn&#39;t see her. I&#39;d get up and her mother, Debbie Reynolds, would shout: &#39;Hey Charlie – you wanna drink?&#39; and I&#39;d say: &#39;No, I&#39;m James, thanks very much,” then head to the studio. A month later, I started to see Carrie more. I came home one night and sat on the end of her bed and we talked until morning. After that, whenever I got back from the studio I&#39;d go into her room to talk, no matter if it was 11pm or 3am. She became my best, best friend.” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Czd6pYLLhNc/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: c